    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏背景</h2>钢铁与魔法并存的蒸汽时代，机器变得越来越强大，并开始有组织地发动攻击。未来的某一天，人类将遭遇机器大军彻底毁灭的命运。<br>来自各个异时空的英雄们受到一位自称为[人类守护者]的使者召唤而来，他们准备集结力量，打败机械怪，阻止悲剧的发生。<br>在浓烟笼罩之下，一场酝酿已久的阴谋正缓缓拉开帷幕……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/19e46b491974b01085c90c7aa783671a.avif?t=1716462241\" width=620 height=154 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点</h2><strong>【蒸汽+齿轮+铆钉=蒸汽朋克】</strong><br>在游戏里面还可以看到星宿、神明等魔法元素，建筑风格也涵盖了19世纪维多利亚时期蒸汽风格的建筑和星宿魔幻的建筑风格，与游戏的剧情故事紧密结合，营造出极具代入感的场景氛围，给予玩家沉浸式的游戏体验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/f0f8ea96316934a21bf27110e98cadf9.poster.avif?t=1716462241\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/f0f8ea96316934a21bf27110e98cadf9.webm?t=1716462241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/f0f8ea96316934a21bf27110e98cadf9.mp4?t=1716462241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>【超过百种卡牌组合】</strong><br>玩家可以通过多种方式收集卡牌，通过不同的组合方式将卡牌进行筛选，在对战过程中通过使用卡牌相互之间的配合完成战斗胜利。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/991bfa7f3480c3d19a81f41583c20c92.poster.avif?t=1716462241\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/991bfa7f3480c3d19a81f41583c20c92.webm?t=1716462241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/991bfa7f3480c3d19a81f41583c20c92.mp4?t=1716462241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>【卡牌技能自定义组合】</strong><br>独创卡牌融合系统，玩家到达指定地点可以获得自由将已有的卡牌进行自定义组合，两张卡牌的功能会进行融合，增加游戏整体策略性，获得变化无穷的卡牌对战体验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/4afc2b308cae3d23f4cbfc12b03bf0ca.poster.avif?t=1716462241\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/4afc2b308cae3d23f4cbfc12b03bf0ca.webm?t=1716462241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/4afc2b308cae3d23f4cbfc12b03bf0ca.mp4?t=1716462241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>【扑朔迷离的随机事件设计】</strong><br>游戏中还有偶然能够碰到的奇遇系统和宝藏系统，通过奇遇的随机事件，玩家有机会获取更多卡牌、获得一定的增益，或者是通过机械库获得金币或需要的卡牌。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/b9d932d62123116a130654ae86470b62.poster.avif?t=1716462241\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/b9d932d62123116a130654ae86470b62.webm?t=1716462241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/b9d932d62123116a130654ae86470b62.mp4?t=1716462241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色介绍</h2><strong>飞行员：</strong><br>来自于蒸汽时代后期。在她的时间线，机械大军已经统治了世界，人类被迫躲藏在地底下。飞行员一直期待着有朝一日能驾驶飞机冲出地底，打败机械军团，拯救世界。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/c450e45778164c57ab3e54c6c7f35177.avif?t=1716462241\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br><strong>武士：</strong><br>武士原本生活于日本战国时代，因受到国君赏识和支持，家族落魄的武士在日复一日的练习中拥有了天下无双的剑技，成为了国君身边最忠诚最厉害的武士。来到蒸汽时代后，一直希望尽快帮忙解决这个世界的问题，找到回去的办法，返回自己的时代。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/5c3230d348c6bbc63e13bd3454ba5b61.avif?t=1716462241\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br><strong>工程师：</strong><br>出生于繁华的蒸汽时代，是位天赋异禀的天才工程师，可以造出任何复杂的机械。整个泽拉姆城的机械化都出自他手，因此，泽拉姆城成为这片大陆上拥有最先进机械技术的城市。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/1aa84ea1def1740d897a647433cdcea4.avif?t=1716462241\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br><strong>机械师：</strong><br>这位寻求刺激的冒险者，与她的机器并肩作战，不断加强她和机器之间的联系，直至两者合而为一。在驾驶她的机甲时，她才感受到生命的激荡。勇敢、果断，她将在战场上助您一臂之力，共同迎接挑战！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/85ae2b7df18ef7c494fd6704ad7a3d69.avif?t=1716462241\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>赌徒：</strong><br>一个秉持虚无主义的冒险者。女赌徒生活在生与死之间的边缘，设法将虚无缥缈的可能性变得对她有利。她永无止境的贪婪使她无法享受已经获得的东西。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861090/extras/6755b04c245d7522a43c5512e7ffbb6a.avif?t=1716462241\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
